*iwl7260-ucode-0.12.16.25 (25 Mar 2015)
*iwl7260-ucode-0.10.15.23 (25 Mar 2015)

  25 Mar 2015; Mark Wright <gienah@gentoo.org> +iwl7260-ucode-0.10.15.23.ebuild,
  +iwl7260-ucode-0.12.16.25.ebuild:
  Bump iwl7260-ucode to 0.10.15.23 (upstream write the version number components
  reversed) for kernel 3.17+ and 0.12.16.25 for kernel 3.19+. Fixes Bug 540316 -
  sys-firmware/iwl7260-ucode-0.10.13.23 version bump - thanks to David Flogeras
  for reporting.

*iwl7260-ucode-0.10.11.23 (14 Jan 2015)
*iwl7260-ucode-0.7.1.22 (14 Jan 2015)
*iwl7260-ucode-0.8.15.22 (14 Jan 2015)
*iwl7260-ucode-0.8.24.22 (14 Jan 2015)
*iwl7260-ucode-0.9.214.23 (14 Jan 2015)
*iwl7260-ucode-0.9.228.25 (14 Jan 2015)

  14 Jan 2015; Mark Wright <gienah@gentoo.org> +iwl7260-ucode-0.10.11.23.ebuild,
  +iwl7260-ucode-0.7.1.22.ebuild, +iwl7260-ucode-0.8.15.22.ebuild,
  +iwl7260-ucode-0.8.24.22.ebuild, +iwl7260-ucode-0.9.214.23.ebuild,
  +iwl7260-ucode-0.9.228.25.ebuild, -iwl7260-ucode-22.1.7.0-r1.ebuild,
  -iwl7260-ucode-22.1.7.0.ebuild, -iwl7260-ucode-22.15.8.0-r1.ebuild,
  -iwl7260-ucode-22.15.8.0.ebuild, -iwl7260-ucode-22.24.8.0.ebuild,
  -iwl7260-ucode-23.214.9.0.ebuild, -iwl7260-ucode-25.228.9.0.ebuild:
  Reverse the version numbers so that users will see an upgrade instead of a
  downgrade, fixes Bug 533334 - sys-firmware/iwl7260-ucode-23.11.10.0 version
  bump.

*iwl7260-ucode-25.228.9.0 (17 Nov 2014)

  17 Nov 2014; Mark Wright <gienah@gentoo.org> +iwl7260-ucode-25.228.9.0.ebuild:
  Thanks to Julian Simioni and David Flogeras for providing the update to
  25.228.9.0, testing and reporting. Fixes bug 528650.

*iwl7260-ucode-23.214.9.0 (16 Jun 2014)

  16 Jun 2014; Mark Wright <gienah@gentoo.org> +iwl7260-ucode-23.214.9.0.ebuild,
  iwl7260-ucode-22.15.8.0-r1.ebuild, iwl7260-ucode-22.15.8.0.ebuild,
  iwl7260-ucode-22.24.8.0.ebuild:
  Bump iwl7260-ucode to 23.214.9.0, thanks to David Flogeras for the ebuild and
  the bump request bug 513212. Fix bug 513216 typos in ebuilds, thanks to David
  Flogeras for reporting and fixing.

*iwl7260-ucode-22.24.8.0 (30 Mar 2014)

  30 Mar 2014; Mark Wright <gienah@gentoo.org> +iwl7260-ucode-22.24.8.0.ebuild:
  Bump iwl7260-ucode to 22.24.8.0 - untested as I do not have access to this
  hardware.

*iwl7260-ucode-22.15.8.0-r1 (25 Jan 2014)
*iwl7260-ucode-22.1.7.0-r1 (25 Jan 2014)

  25 Jan 2014; Mark Wright <gienah@gentoo.org>
  +iwl7260-ucode-22.1.7.0-r1.ebuild, +iwl7260-ucode-22.15.8.0-r1.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Add bluetooth use flag to pull in sys-firmware/iwl3160-7260-bt-ucode for the
  Intel Wireless Bluetooth 3160 and Intel Wireless Bluetooth 7260 devices. Part
  of bug #489714, thanks to Thomas Kear for reporting, testing and initial
  ebuilds.

  23 Jan 2014; Mark Wright <gienah@gentoo.org> iwl7260-ucode-22.15.8.0.ebuild:
  Thanks to Thomas Kear for testing and this fix (for my copy-paste bug): sys-
  firmware/iwl7260-ucode-22.15.8.0: Fails on doins, filename is
  iwlwifi-7260-8.ucode not iwlwifi-7260-7.ucode in this version.

  23 Jan 2014; Mark Wright <gienah@gentoo.org> iwl7260-ucode-22.1.7.0.ebuild,
  iwl7260-ucode-22.15.8.0.ebuild:
  Thanks to Thomas Kear for the fix: SRC_URI needs a -> to avoid ugly download
  filenames. Part of bug #489714.

*iwl7260-ucode-22.1.7.0 (23 Jan 2014)
*iwl7260-ucode-22.15.8.0 (23 Jan 2014)

  23 Jan 2014; Mark Wright <gienah@gentoo.org> +iwl7260-ucode-22.1.7.0.ebuild,
  +iwl7260-ucode-22.15.8.0.ebuild, +metadata.xml:
